title.rendered: BOSS AIR DIGITAL AIRBAG INFLATION KIT PX01

content.rendered:
BOSS AIR DIGITAL AIRBAG INFLATION KIT PX01

Boss Air Digital Airbag Inflation Kit PX01 available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

This Digital kit is used to control Boss Load Assist Kits or airbag suspension from inside your cab without the need for a tank and running air line inside.

Simple installation with control of airbags UP and down using Boss Air’s PX01 compressor. Comes with twin LED 200psi readout gauge.

This Kit includes;

  • 1 x PX-01 12V BOSS Air Compressor
  • 1 x Gauge panel
  • 2 x Blue LED Push buttons for up and down
  • 1 x BOSS 200psi Twin readout digital gauge
  • 2 x Boss Mini 12v air valves with fittings
  • 10 meters of 1/4” J844 DOT Airbrake line
  • 1 x 1/4” push connect Y check valve
  • 2 x T Connectors for sender units
  • 4 x T Connectors
  • 10 x Cable Ties
  • 1 x tube sealant
  • Instruction Sheet
To view the range of Boss Air products available, CLICK HERE!
Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!
